{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 210101, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 38050, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为啥要喝热水您知道吗", "timestamp": 1596507157, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210103, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 38050, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "喝热水好像是建国那会防流行病开始提的，对于以前水净化不好的情况来说，开水肯定比生水不知道好到哪去了，不过现在都有净水机，别太烫就行吧", "timestamp": 1596507177, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210109, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 38050, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "开国初期，毛建议水高温烧开杀死细菌。在那个物质匮乏的年代避免了大量的疾病", "timestamp": 1596507247, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210111, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 38050, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是建国后卫生运动提倡的吧，当时自来水的普及和洁净程度都有限，当然也有中国喝热茶饮料传统的因素在内。", "timestamp": 1596507265, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 210112, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 38050, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "三个问号显得您不太有常识", "timestamp": 1596507272, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 38050, "reply": 5, "tag": null, "text": "#37954\n喝热水是西医的提倡吗？？？", "timestamp": 1596507056, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782599, "url": "", "vote": {}}}